headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Bullish on W.W. Grainger Stock?
summary: W.W. Grainger has underperformed the broader market over the past year, and analysts are cautious about the stock’s prospects.

headline: 1 Industrials Stock with Solid Fundamentals and 2 We Brush Off
summary: Whether you see them or not, industrials businesses play a crucial part in our daily activities. They are also bound to benefit from a friendlier regulatory environment with the Trump administration, and this excitement has led to a six-month gain of 20.4% for the sector - higher than the S&P 500’s 6.5% return.
